layout: layout.njk
title: Welcome in!
---

<p>Ahoy! <br /><br /> Welcome to FREEMOTES, the home of free emotes for everyone to use on Twitch. These have all been created by <a href="https://www.twitch.tv/gromfalloon/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">me</a> to share with the world. I want people having fun emotes to use, regardless of budget. The world is better with art in it!</p>

<h2>Recent ✨</h2>


{% set sortedEmotes = collections.emotes | sort(attribute="data.date") | reverse %}

<div class="grid" id="emoteGrid">
  {% set sortedEmotes = collections.emotes | reverse %}
  {% for emote in sortedEmotes.slice(0, 5) %}
    {% if emote.inputPath != "./src/emotes/index.md" %}
      {% set tags = emote.data.tags or [] %}
      <a
        class="card"
        href="{{ emote.url }}"
        data-tags="{{ tags | join(' ') | lower }}"
      >
        <img src="{{ emote.data.image }}" alt="{{ emote.data.title }}" width="112" height="112">
      </a>
    {% endif %}
  {% endfor %}
</div>

